.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE-SPLICE-STATUS" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-splice-status \- show channels currently in splice negotiation
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-splice-status
.SH DESCRIPTION
Returns channels whose state contains SPLICING.
.PP
Output:
.nf
{"splicing_count":N, "channels":[{channel_id, state}]}
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-channel-pending (1)
